Nearly a century after magic was recognized as a real form of technology, Miyuki Shiba begins her term at Magic High School. An honor student, she dreamed of enjoying school with her older brother Tatsuya, an irregular student. But a rift between the gifted Course 1 students and the inferior Course 2 students could stand in the way. This time, Miyuki is the star of the show!
(Source: Funimation)
The third season of Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei. After the battle against The New Breed Front, Tatsuya and Miyuki enter the new "Magic Engineering Department." (Source: Crunchyroll)
Isekai de Cheat Skill wo Te ni Shita Ore wa, Genjitsu Sekai wo mo Musou Suru: Level Up wa Jinsei wo Kaeta

Its time for the Ousei Academy camping trip! Yuuya and his classmates head into the wilderness, where theyll need to build shelters, find food, and otherwise fend for themselves. Yuuya quickly steals the show (and several of his classmates hearts) after saving the day, thanks to his maxed-out survival skills! And back in the other world, the day Yuuya promised to meet Princess Lexia has arrived. But an ambush cuts their reunion short when Luna moves to complete her mission and assassinate the princess! As Yuuya recalls their time training together in the forestand the bond they forgedwill he be able to do whats necessary to stop her?
(Source: Yen Press)

Hwa-Jin Nas teaching techniques are pretty violent for someone who works in the Ministry of Education. That being said, when punishments don't seem to work on even the worst of school bullies, there is no better man for the job. Sometimes you cant get a good education until those bullies are taught a lesson. (Source: WEBTOONS, edited) Note: Belongs to Blue String universe.
